In one ear and out the other.

10
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:30,390
I'm great at that.

11
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:33,830
Nothing bothers you, huh?

12
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:34,770
I envy you.

13
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:38,090
