20
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:07,940
It's the same for everyone.

21
00:01:07,950 --> 00:01:10,270
It's not just you.

22
00:01:11,370 --> 00:01:13,190
Gwangbak, don't worry.

23
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:15,590
There's something you can try.

24
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,740
What is it?

25
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:20,060
How to be friends with your mother in law.

26
00:01:33,550 --> 00:01:35,300
Honey.

27
