- Don't?
- That will drive him mad.

33
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:59,490
Okay. I got it.

34
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,300
- The person you have called...
- Man!

35
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,640
After the beep...

36
00:03:02,650 --> 00:03:03,890
Man!

37
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:17,030
Answer it this time.

38
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:20,640
- What is it?
- Where are you?

39
00:03:20,650 --> 00:03:23,100
What do you think?

40
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:25,770
At a karaoke place.
Near the shop.

41
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:28,830
Hobak! Have a drink!

42
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:32,140
Hobak! It's your turn to sing.

43
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:36,100
Sing a song! Sing a song! Sing a song!

44
00:03:36,110 --> 00:03:38,340
Aren't you supposed to be working?

45
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:40,330
I'm busy. I have to sing. Bye.

46
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:43,600
Hey! Hey! You! You! Hey!

47
00:03:43,610 --> 00:03:45,800
I don't believe...

48
